{
  "abandonment_by_lack_of_transparency": "She will abandon due to Lack of Transparency: If a feature presents a 'magic' insight without providing a clear, accessible way to see the underlying data and methodology, she will immediately reject it. Her log will read: 'This AI Insight is a black box. It's useless to me because I can't verify its accuracy. Terminating evaluation.'",
